query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!: i64"
        FROM projects
        WHERE is_active = true
          AND ($1::uuid IS NULL OR owner_id = $1)
          AND ($2::text IS NULL OR visibility = $2)
          AND ($3::text IS NULL OR name ILIKE $3)
          AND (
              visibility = 'public'
              OR visibility = 'internal'
              OR owner_id = $4
          )
